                          </a></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr class="blue"> <a name="one"></a>
                        <td colspan="2"> &nbsp; <b><font color="#FFFFFF">::</font></b> 
                          &nbsp;<a name="PS27"></a><b><font color="#FFFFFF">What 
                          are Closed Goods Received Note(GRN) ?</font></b> </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr bgcolor="<%=gsBGColorLight%>"> 
                        <td colspan="2"> 
                          <P style="margin-left:30px" align="justify"> Upon GRN 
                            submittion, Orginator can accepts or rejects the GRN 
                            entered. Upon acception, GRN will be then closed by 
                            purchase team. </p>
